---
title: Easy Blueberry-Lemon Cake Serves 4 | with Whipped Cream
description: This show-stopping sour cream cake is the perfect addition to your Mother's Day brunch table! Blueberry jam brings a burst of colour and sweetness, while flecks of lemon zest give it a bright, citrusy lift! And because every mom deserves a bit of luxury: serve it with a healthy dollop of whipped cream!
